des:
Ask for anji chary Facts, and learn about what really matters, like dark matter.

anji chary Facts provides fun the whole family can enjoy and is guaranteed to make you smarter.

To start, just say "Alexa, launch anji chary Facts" or "Alexa, open anji chary Facts" to get a fact".

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
